00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:43.680
[Episode 7]

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:49.350
Zhaoyuan.

00:01:50.870 --> 00:01:53.000
Fine, Zhou Zhaoyuan, Zhou Zhaoyuan.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:55.120
I want to apply to military school

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:57.039
and serve on the front lines
against the Japanese.

00:01:57.039 --> 00:01:57.820
That's great.

00:01:57.820 --> 00:02:00.380
Then you're sure
to become an excellent soldier.

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:01.790
Don't laugh. I mean it.

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:03.150
I mean it, too.

00:02:03.510 --> 00:02:04.590
If you need it,

00:02:04.590 --> 00:02:06.530
I'll write you a recommendation letter.

00:02:06.530 --> 00:02:10.520
Right now, all I want is to graduate
from middle school as soon as possible.

00:02:10.520 --> 00:02:11.630
There was a man in the Song dynasty

00:02:11.630 --> 00:02:13.810
who saw his crops weren't growing,
so he pulled them up

00:02:13.810 --> 00:02:14.960
and went home exhausted.

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:16.090
What does that mean?

00:02:16.710 --> 00:02:18.630
Pulling up seedlings
to help them grow never works.

00:02:18.630 --> 00:02:19.400
See?

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.450
You really should read more books.

00:02:22.150 --> 00:02:23.150
I'm done with you.

00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:26.800
Are you mad?

00:02:26.829 --> 00:02:27.300
No.

00:02:31.090 --> 00:02:33.350
I'll take you out for butterfly cookies.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:34.670
Two boxes.

00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:35.120
Okay.

00:02:35.150 --> 00:02:35.980
Deal.

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:39.750
Let's go.

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:56.040
Thanks for helping me this time.

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:01.730
What do you mean?

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:03.770
It's a gift for your grand opening.

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:19.910
Have a seat.

00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:34.550
I'm sorry.

00:03:35.430 --> 00:03:37.079
I used to be selfish

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:38.750
and foolish,

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:41.630
always blind to my own faults.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.730
Coming back to the old house

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:50.400
seeing it like this

00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:54.240
makes me truly happy.

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:58.160
And seeing
your maternity hospital doing so well,

00:03:58.630 --> 00:03:59.590
I'm genuinely

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:01.060
happy for you, too.

00:04:02.590 --> 00:04:03.400
I mean it.

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:06.640
Since Mom is staying at your place,

00:04:08.110 --> 00:04:09.840
you should take good care of her.

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:10.640
I understand.

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:12.070
Mom's staying with me

00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:15.030
and is being well taken care of,

00:04:15.030 --> 00:04:16.120
so don't worry.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:17.850
Your sister-in-law

00:04:18.070 --> 00:04:19.399
cooks three meals a day,

00:04:19.760 --> 00:04:21.560
and all of them Mom's favorites.

00:04:22.790 --> 00:04:24.070
When I have time,

00:04:24.430 --> 00:04:25.960
I also take her out for walks

00:04:26.270 --> 00:04:27.100
and chats.

00:04:28.270 --> 00:04:29.430
Mom's really happy.

00:04:30.310 --> 00:04:31.710
It's just that sometimes

00:04:33.270 --> 00:04:34.640
she talks to herself,

00:04:35.070 --> 00:04:36.600
saying she misses you a lot.

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.440
Why don't you go visit her

00:04:41.750 --> 00:04:42.950
when you're not busy?

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:50.750
I'm really sorry.

00:04:57.870 --> 00:04:58.830
This gift

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.430
isn't expensive.

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:03.770
Just think of it as a small token

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:06.950
of my appreciation for your grand opening,

00:05:06.950 --> 00:05:07.600
okay?

00:05:25.460 --> 00:05:27.270
Please take good care of Meina.

00:05:28.190 --> 00:05:29.500
She's very delicate,

00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:31.390
and since it's her first pregnancy,

00:05:31.390 --> 00:05:32.750
please look after her.

00:05:33.400 --> 00:05:34.040
Meina?

00:05:35.430 --> 00:05:36.240
Shao Meina?

00:05:37.770 --> 00:05:39.680
The relative
Sis brought over yesterday?

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:40.390
Yeah.

00:05:40.630 --> 00:05:42.630
What's your relationship with her?

00:05:51.950 --> 00:05:53.670
No, our mom

00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:55.500
is really happy this time.

00:05:57.680 --> 00:05:58.310
I mean...

00:05:58.600 --> 00:05:59.530
Mom asked

00:05:59.630 --> 00:06:01.070
if you could

00:06:01.070 --> 00:06:02.360
waive that fee for her.

00:06:04.010 --> 00:06:04.830
We're all family.

00:06:04.830 --> 00:06:06.460
Can't you just waive the fee?

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:25.560
Sis,

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:26.720
what are you doing?

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:27.630
Siyun is here.

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:31.420
Her feet are swollen,
so I'm soaking them for her.

00:06:31.420 --> 00:06:32.820
Come with me to my office.

00:06:33.510 --> 00:06:34.750
You go ahead then.

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:37.600
When you come back,
peel two apples for me.

00:06:39.110 --> 00:06:40.110
Get out of the way.

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:49.630
What are you looking at?

00:06:49.630 --> 00:06:51.230
I'm not done washing my feet.

00:06:52.360 --> 00:06:53.360
I'll help you.

00:06:54.870 --> 00:06:56.600
Why are you so afraid of your sister?

00:06:56.600 --> 00:06:58.730
Didn't you say this hospital is yours?

00:06:59.190 --> 00:07:01.040
She's just helping you out, isn't she?

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:02.240
I'm not afraid of her.

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:03.900
She's my little sister.

00:07:04.170 --> 00:07:05.430
I was being nice to her.

00:07:05.630 --> 00:07:07.360
You're not lying to me, are you?

00:07:07.430 --> 00:07:08.790
Why would I lie to you?

00:07:09.190 --> 00:07:11.990
I've been running this hospital
for quite a while.

00:07:20.420 --> 00:07:21.820
Why did you wash her feet?

00:07:23.800 --> 00:07:24.830
All I can do

00:07:24.830 --> 00:07:27.000
is take care of the Lin family.

00:07:27.330 --> 00:07:29.430
You don't need to do things like that!

00:07:30.630 --> 00:07:31.510
It's fine.

00:07:31.710 --> 00:07:32.570
I can endure it.

00:07:32.750 --> 00:07:33.750
You can endure it?

00:07:34.510 --> 00:07:35.409
For how long?

00:07:36.510 --> 00:07:37.480
For a lifetime?

00:07:46.430 --> 00:07:47.800
I'll endure it...

00:07:48.950 --> 00:07:50.300
for as long as it takes.

00:08:38.940 --> 00:08:39.740
Mr. Cheng.

00:08:49.030 --> 00:08:50.440
One of the few optimists.

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:53.820
I'd like to ask you a favor.

00:08:54.190 --> 00:08:55.650
Some of my student friends

00:08:55.720 --> 00:08:58.450
want to join
the volunteer army in the northeast.

00:08:58.670 --> 00:08:59.630
Wu Xiaoshan?

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:00.350
Yes.

00:09:00.750 --> 00:09:01.480
Sure,

00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:03.390
I'll make the arrangements.

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:04.360
Thank you.

00:09:04.840 --> 00:09:06.570
I'd like to ask you a favor, too.

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:08.550
We urgently need a batch of medicine

00:09:08.550 --> 00:09:09.880
and medical equipment.

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:15.240
Here's the medicine list and the deposit.

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:16.270
I only have one month

00:09:16.270 --> 00:09:18.600
to gather and send them
to the front lines.

00:09:28.440 --> 00:09:30.840
It's not easy to find
such a large quantity

00:09:31.080 --> 00:09:32.610
of medicine and equipment.

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:36.400
I'll figure something out.

00:09:38.530 --> 00:09:39.530
Keep the money.

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:40.970
I'll cover the cost.

00:09:41.390 --> 00:09:42.840
That's a lot of money.

00:09:42.990 --> 00:09:45.190
Consider it a token of my appreciation.

00:09:46.270 --> 00:09:47.080
Fine.

00:09:48.180 --> 00:09:49.110
I'll contact you

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:50.200
in a month.

00:09:51.750 --> 00:09:52.350
Take care.

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:12.630
Cheng Ao, Cheng Ao.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:14.250
Come and eat.

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:27.200
You're back.

00:10:28.320 --> 00:10:29.510
Why didn't you tell us in advance?

00:10:29.510 --> 00:10:30.910
I wanted to surprise you.

00:10:32.510 --> 00:10:33.410
Go get Master.

00:10:33.800 --> 00:10:34.360
Okay.

00:10:34.630 --> 00:10:37.270
Come try my pickled cabbage pork stew.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:39.360
This pot, half a pig,

00:10:39.570 --> 00:10:40.840
and a few pounds of pickled cabbageâ€”

00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:42.950
I carried them all back
from the Northeast.

00:10:42.950 --> 00:10:43.630
Here.

00:10:46.390 --> 00:10:48.030
Did you go to the Northeast to be a chef?

00:10:48.030 --> 00:10:49.030
Of course not.

00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:51.750
I only cook for family.

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:03.630
Dad.

00:11:11.390 --> 00:11:12.200
You're back.

00:11:13.700 --> 00:11:15.240
You're only back because
you squandered all your money, right?

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:16.240
No, that's not it.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:20.150
Call her Mom.

00:11:24.150 --> 00:11:24.630
Mom.

00:11:26.630 --> 00:11:27.490
It's your turn.

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:30.460
Madam Yanhong.

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:34.550
This is Dalun.

00:11:35.080 --> 00:11:37.550
But don't believe

00:11:37.550 --> 00:11:38.350
a word he says.

00:11:39.480 --> 00:11:40.790
This is Cheng Ao,

00:11:40.790 --> 00:11:42.360
our family's great lawyer.

00:11:47.140 --> 00:11:48.840
Father, you're really something.

00:11:48.840 --> 00:11:49.870
I just got back,

00:11:50.390 --> 00:11:51.180
and suddenly
there's another little brother.

00:11:51.180 --> 00:11:52.650
You're still
so full of energy at your age.

00:11:52.650 --> 00:11:53.650
Enough nonsense.

00:11:54.200 --> 00:11:56.550
Say it. Why are you back this time?

00:11:56.550 --> 00:11:58.150
I came back to look after you.

00:11:58.850 --> 00:12:00.650
I can't afford that kind of care.

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:01.870
Seriously,

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:03.160
I came back

00:12:03.190 --> 00:12:04.990
with a government job this time.

00:12:06.120 --> 00:12:07.270
Wherever you work,

00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:10.800
don't cause me any more trouble.

00:12:11.670 --> 00:12:12.400
Don't worry.

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:14.540
It's good to have you back.

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:17.840
How were things
with the Japanese in the Northeast?

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.200
Cheng Ao, what are you talking about?

00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:20.870
How could I ever have dealings with them?

00:12:20.870 --> 00:12:22.270
Dad taught us from childhood

00:12:22.270 --> 00:12:24.070
never to deal with the Japanese.

00:12:24.080 --> 00:12:26.010
Dad, I've always kept that in mind.

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:30.320
So, what did you cook?

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:31.060
Let me see.

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:37.680
Have a seat, Yanhong.

00:12:38.030 --> 00:12:38.600
Dalun,

00:12:39.630 --> 00:12:41.600
have the brothers sit and eat.

00:12:42.020 --> 00:12:44.020
Everyone, come sit and keep eating.

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:46.840
Cheng Ao,

00:12:47.120 --> 00:12:48.580
I was gone for just a while,

00:12:48.670 --> 00:12:50.400
and now I have another brother?

00:12:51.750 --> 00:12:52.840
How would I know?

00:12:53.030 --> 00:12:54.960
It's my first time seeing her, too.

00:12:56.030 --> 00:12:57.430
How do you know it's a boy?

00:12:59.550 --> 00:13:01.350
I've actually looked into this.

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:03.030
If the belly is pointy, it's a boy.

00:13:03.030 --> 00:13:04.490
If it's round, it's a girl.

00:13:05.360 --> 00:13:06.020
Hurry up.

00:13:06.050 --> 00:13:06.600
Coming.

00:13:12.070 --> 00:13:12.920
Here, Father.

00:13:14.470 --> 00:13:15.080
Here, Mom.

00:13:15.100 --> 00:13:16.020
Thank you.

00:13:19.650 --> 00:13:20.710
Thank you, my dear.

00:13:21.810 --> 00:13:22.240
Dad.

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:24.600
Why not sit there?

00:13:25.150 --> 00:13:27.680
I just got back,
so I wanted to sit close to you.

00:13:29.720 --> 00:13:30.580
Aren't you hot?

00:13:38.630 --> 00:13:40.030
This jacket's yours now.

00:13:45.510 --> 00:13:46.120
Is it good?

00:13:51.630 --> 00:13:53.430
Did you rob a salt vendor or what?

00:13:56.260 --> 00:13:57.240
Try it yourself.

00:14:01.870 --> 00:14:03.030
Yeah, it seems a bit salty.

00:14:03.030 --> 00:14:03.910
Just a bit?

00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:05.800
Don't drink too much.

00:14:08.480 --> 00:14:11.280
[Sinan Maternity Hospital]

00:14:15.150 --> 00:14:16.030
Who are you?

00:14:16.390 --> 00:14:17.990
I'm Lin Jinghan's daughter.

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:20.630
Oh, it's you.
Lin Jinghan told me about you.

00:14:20.630 --> 00:14:22.320
I brought you some food.

00:14:23.720 --> 00:14:25.450
Did you make all this yourself?

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:27.750
There are vegetables, meat, and soup.

00:14:27.750 --> 00:14:28.550
Go ahead, eat.

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:30.260
You're so thoughtful.

00:14:30.460 --> 00:14:31.260
My dad said

00:14:31.290 --> 00:14:32.690
we should treat you well.

00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:40.240
Things were better before.

00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:42.200
At least this house was still ours.

00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:45.480
What did you say?

00:14:47.050 --> 00:14:48.410
When Grandpa was alive,

00:14:48.430 --> 00:14:50.030
our family was very wealthy.

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:51.600
Later, my grandpa passed away,

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:53.000
and my dad ran up a lot of debt,

00:14:53.000 --> 00:14:55.460
so this house was mortgaged
to his creditor.

00:14:55.530 --> 00:14:57.640
He used all the money
from selling the house to pay off debts.

00:14:57.640 --> 00:14:59.000
Not a single penny was left.

00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:01.790
He still hasn't paid off the bank loans.

00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:03.790
My dad's broke.

00:15:03.810 --> 00:15:05.480
He's got nothing but debt.

00:15:06.390 --> 00:15:08.390
You're saying Lin Jinghan's broke?

00:15:09.240 --> 00:15:10.790
Isn't this hospital his?

00:15:10.840 --> 00:15:12.270
This hospital isn't my father's.

00:15:12.270 --> 00:15:13.630
It belongs to my aunt.

00:15:13.630 --> 00:15:15.230
It has nothing to do with him.

00:15:15.590 --> 00:15:18.390
He still owes the money
for your hospitalization.

00:15:21.480 --> 00:15:22.080
Dad.

00:15:23.920 --> 00:15:25.250
What are you doing here?

00:15:26.030 --> 00:15:27.360
I came to bring her food.

00:15:27.710 --> 00:15:29.310
Food's here. I'll get going.

00:15:33.550 --> 00:15:34.880
Come, sit here.

00:15:35.870 --> 00:15:37.330
What did she come here for?

00:15:37.550 --> 00:15:39.110
Your daughter just told me

00:15:39.600 --> 00:15:40.660
that you're broke,

00:15:41.240 --> 00:15:42.940
and this hospital isn't yours either.

00:15:42.940 --> 00:15:44.400
Was she telling the truth?

00:15:44.930 --> 00:15:46.170
Of course not!

00:15:46.670 --> 00:15:47.670
She lied to you.

00:15:48.240 --> 00:15:49.970
That kid never tells the truth.

00:15:51.550 --> 00:15:54.080
Jinghan, be honest with me.

00:15:55.240 --> 00:15:56.480
I'm with you,

00:15:56.840 --> 00:15:58.120
carrying your baby

00:15:58.600 --> 00:16:00.460
because I love you for who you are,

00:16:01.300 --> 00:16:02.390
not for your money.

00:16:03.240 --> 00:16:04.510
Even if you're broke,

00:16:04.790 --> 00:16:05.720
it doesn't matter.

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:07.250
We can still earn together.

00:16:07.480 --> 00:16:09.080
But I hope the one I love

00:16:09.240 --> 00:16:10.720
tells me the truth

00:16:10.860 --> 00:16:11.880
and doesn't lie.

00:16:18.060 --> 00:16:19.390
I'll tell you the truth.

00:16:20.670 --> 00:16:21.950
Promise you won't get mad?

00:16:21.950 --> 00:16:22.660
Sure.

00:16:22.960 --> 00:16:25.290
Couples should be honest with each other.

00:16:32.390 --> 00:16:32.990
Yes,

00:16:35.750 --> 00:16:36.890
I did lie to you.

00:16:38.510 --> 00:16:40.440
But wasn't that because I love you?

00:16:40.610 --> 00:16:41.010
I...

00:16:42.520 --> 00:16:43.800
I just...

00:16:44.250 --> 00:16:46.110
I was just afraid that in my state,

00:16:46.270 --> 00:16:47.150
I'd lose you.

00:16:52.150 --> 00:16:53.680
I'm not having this baby!

00:16:55.490 --> 00:16:57.890
I never should've married
a woman like you.

00:17:11.440 --> 00:17:12.240
Sis,

00:17:13.510 --> 00:17:14.829
I don't pity you.

00:17:16.060 --> 00:17:17.210
I care about you.

00:17:18.470 --> 00:17:21.859
I know you want to be
a good daughter-in-law to the Lin family,

00:17:21.859 --> 00:17:23.790
and a good mother to your children.

00:17:25.030 --> 00:17:27.089
But sometimes, when it's necessary,

00:17:27.480 --> 00:17:28.680
you need to be selfish

00:17:29.350 --> 00:17:31.080
and think more about yourself.

00:17:31.750 --> 00:17:33.280
I understand what you mean.

00:17:34.240 --> 00:17:35.840
I've thought about that too.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:40.290
Whenever Lin Jinghan acts ridiculously,

00:17:40.290 --> 00:17:41.940
I really want to take my kids

00:17:42.070 --> 00:17:44.440
and leave the Lin family
without looking back.

00:17:44.440 --> 00:17:45.720
But where could I go?

00:17:46.240 --> 00:17:47.640
Back to my parents' home?

00:17:47.790 --> 00:17:50.400
I can already picture the villagers

00:17:50.420 --> 00:17:52.250
drowning me with their gossip.

00:17:54.510 --> 00:17:56.110
I can hardly support myself.

00:17:56.790 --> 00:17:59.920
I can't let my kids suffer with me, can I?

00:18:01.480 --> 00:18:02.810
It's not that you can'tâ€”

00:18:03.560 --> 00:18:04.690
you just don't dare.

00:18:05.720 --> 00:18:06.830
You still have me.

00:18:08.070 --> 00:18:09.830
Mom, I avenged you.

00:18:10.760 --> 00:18:11.760
What do you mean?

00:18:11.790 --> 00:18:12.930
You'll see when we get there.

00:18:12.930 --> 00:18:13.460
Let's go.

00:18:14.290 --> 00:18:14.820
Hurry up.

00:18:32.070 --> 00:18:33.530
Why is your nose bleeding?

