I'm going to see a movie.

00:37:38.480 --> 00:37:39.280
Sis,

00:37:39.560 --> 00:37:40.670
I really didn't expect

00:37:40.670 --> 00:37:42.330
Yi could convince you and Mom.

00:37:43.020 --> 00:37:44.220
I'm quite surprised.

00:37:45.110 --> 00:37:47.150
She's your mother's eldest grandchild.

00:37:47.150 --> 00:37:48.480
Don't you know her well?

00:37:50.550 --> 00:37:51.320
Siyun.

00:37:51.840 --> 00:37:53.700
I don't know anything about this.

00:37:54.000 --> 00:37:55.150
Can I really make it?

00:37:57.780 --> 00:37:58.590
Sis,

00:37:59.070 --> 00:38:00.070
don't be nervous.

00:38:00.360 --> 00:38:01.890
I'll teach you step by step.

00:38:03.730 --> 00:38:04.410
Siyun,

00:38:04.440 --> 00:38:05.400
thank you.

00:38:06.480 --> 00:38:07.810
Don't be formal with me.

00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:09.550
Alright, I won't be formal then.

00:38:09.550 --> 00:38:11.510
I'll definitely try my best to learn.

00:38:11.510 --> 00:38:12.030
Let's go

00:38:12.230 --> 00:38:12.760
Let's go.

00:38:16.110 --> 00:38:18.040
Dalun, what happened to your hand?

00:38:20.320 --> 00:38:21.120
It's nothing.

00:38:21.550 --> 00:38:23.150
I got injured during a mission.

00:38:23.150 --> 00:38:25.150
It's good that it's nothing serious.

00:38:25.150 --> 00:38:26.800
I have something to tell both of you.

00:38:26.800 --> 00:38:28.280
We've recently received intel

00:38:28.280 --> 00:38:29.680
that the Communist Party

00:38:29.760 --> 00:38:32.470
is planning several
large-scale operations in Shanghai.

00:38:32.470 --> 00:38:33.880
I want both of you to investigate it.

00:38:33.880 --> 00:38:35.000
You must find out

00:38:35.000 --> 00:38:36.800
exactly what they're plotting.

00:38:36.880 --> 00:38:37.550
Director,

00:38:37.550 --> 00:38:39.070
I've received intel on this too.

00:38:39.070 --> 00:38:40.230
The moment I got the message,

00:38:40.230 --> 00:38:41.510
I sent people to investigate.

00:38:41.510 --> 00:38:43.440
I believe we'll have results soon.

00:38:44.880 --> 00:38:45.320
Jin.

00:38:51.880 --> 00:38:52.880
This is a list

00:38:54.840 --> 00:38:57.040
of Communists I've recently captured,

00:39:00.110 --> 00:39:02.190
including some pro-Communist people.

00:39:02.190 --> 00:39:03.510
Recruit those we can,

00:39:03.670 --> 00:39:04.600
and for the rest,

00:39:05.110 --> 00:39:06.590
arrest them all.

00:39:06.670 --> 00:39:08.200
Those who resist publicly,

00:39:09.070 --> 00:39:10.590
kill them all.

00:39:10.930 --> 00:39:11.410
But...

00:39:12.000 --> 00:39:13.600
do not reveal your identity.

00:39:17.590 --> 00:39:18.400
Yiqun,

00:39:19.440 --> 00:39:21.970
Dalun's been working
at the periphery for us.

00:39:22.280 --> 00:39:23.610
You two must stay united

00:39:26.630 --> 00:39:27.960
and work diligently together.

00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:31.090
The organization is fair
with rewards and punishments.

00:39:31.550 --> 00:39:32.950
Director, rest assured,

00:39:33.000 --> 00:39:34.110
we'll work hard

00:39:35.400 --> 00:39:36.330
and stay united.

00:39:39.210 --> 00:39:40.250
Good. Cheers.

00:39:47.450 --> 00:39:49.540
[Light Theater]

00:39:58.770 --> 00:40:01.400
About that batch of medicine
you mentioned last time,

00:40:01.400 --> 00:40:02.930
I've thought of a solution.

00:40:03.750 --> 00:40:05.480
Sichuan is currently

00:40:05.510 --> 00:40:08.230
suffering from famine and plague.

00:40:08.560 --> 00:40:10.720
We can hold a charity fundraiser

00:40:11.630 --> 00:40:14.560
for the disaster victims
under the hospital's name.

00:40:14.880 --> 00:40:17.140
First, we can actually help the victims.

00:40:17.280 --> 00:40:19.330
Second, it gives you a cover

00:40:19.360 --> 00:40:22.030
to collect the medicine
and equipment you need.

00:40:22.570 --> 00:40:24.740
You can blend in legitimately

00:40:25.110 --> 00:40:27.070
without arousing suspicion.

00:40:31.000 --> 00:40:32.200
I thought of that too.

00:40:34.280 --> 00:40:35.680
With such a large demand,

00:40:36.280 --> 00:40:38.590
a charity fundraiser is the only option.

00:40:39.630 --> 00:40:41.070
And with this excuse,

00:40:42.140 --> 00:40:44.870
we can also contact
the local Red Cross hospital.

00:40:45.030 --> 00:40:45.960
They must have

00:40:46.760 --> 00:40:49.090
a large quantity of this type of medicine.

00:40:49.800 --> 00:40:51.230
We're on the same page.

00:40:52.360 --> 00:40:54.360
That solves the supply problem.

00:40:55.670 --> 00:40:57.670
But with the current drug controls,

00:40:58.130 --> 00:41:00.480
have you figured out how to

00:41:00.480 --> 00:41:03.010
move them from Shanghai
to your destination?

00:41:04.670 --> 00:41:05.480
Not yet.

00:41:07.960 --> 00:41:09.560
Let's watch the movie first.

00:41:47.880 --> 00:41:49.280
Someone's following us.

00:41:49.590 --> 00:41:50.250
Don't look.

00:41:52.150 --> 00:41:54.080
It could be one of Zeng Dalun's men.

00:42:17.440 --> 00:42:18.230
Cheng Ao,

00:42:19.680 --> 00:42:21.080
your hands are sweating.

00:42:25.630 --> 00:42:28.430
There's no Zeng Dalun's people
here at all, right?

00:42:35.410 --> 00:42:36.610
Maybe I was mistaken.

00:42:40.230 --> 00:42:42.320
It's nice holding hands
while watching a movie like this.